nodes.description: Identify the best tool to archive a webpage.
nodes.agent_prompt: Given the goal 'Archive page https://example.com', identify the most suitable agent or tool for archiving a webpage. Consider available tools for web interaction and content capture. Respond with the name of the tool.

nodes.description: Archive the specified webpage using the identified tool.
nodes.agent_prompt: Archive the webpage located at 'https://example.com' using the `archive_url` tool. Ensure the full content of the page is captured. The output should be a confirmation of the archival action or any relevant archival identifier.

nodes.description: Format the archival result for the user.
nodes.agent_prompt: Present the archival result. If the archival was successful, confirm the action. If there were any issues, report them clearly. Use the 'archival_result_T002' to inform the output.
